result.formatted_address: Hang Fai Building, 127B Third St, Sai Ying Pun, Hong Kong
result.name: Shop9 Restaurant and Lounge

reviews.text: Laidback and comfy. Come on a weekday evening and you’ll definitely find yourself comfortably seated at the open area of a balcony where you can step outside for alfresco dining, or look down on a street corner. You can also dine in the cosy indoor space. Food is great and they serve a wide range of foreign craft beer I’d love to try out. Worth coming back
TASTE FOOD & NICE SERVICE !
Above average food. Great variety of beers.

Excellent service, attentive to our dog as well in the outdoor space. Amazingly cheap for the options and quality!! S$98 plus 10% for salad bar buffet, soup of the day, bread, main course (lamb racks, steak options are available too!) Beyobd our expectation. Will definitely revisit!
Very cosy environment, food is OK. But it's worth it as not pricey for such environment.
